==English==

===Noun===
'''clusterfuck'''

# {{vulgar}} A particular type of [[orgy]], typically consisting of four or more people one behind the other, each one performing [[anal sex]] on the one in front''
# {{vulgar}} A generic term for an [[orgy]].
# {{vulgar}} A disastrously unsuccessful collaborative effort.
#: ''The project looked good at the start, but the manager couldn't coordinate for shit and it ended up a complete clusterfuck.''
# {{vulgar}} A disastrously incompetent person.
#: ''That new manager is a complete clusterfuck.''
# {{vulgar}} A complicated mess of roadways, railroads, or other infrastructure.
# {{vulgar}} Multiple major problems happening concurrently, or in rapid succession.

== Etymology ==

Reportedly coined by hippie poet Ed Sanders in the 1960s.  The original form was
"Mongolian clusterfuck". It was frequently used in the military.

An infamous photograph by [[Robert Mapplethorpe]] shows a half-dozen black and white gay men performing a clusterfuck.

